msgid "The tap detection parameters."
msgstr "轻触检测参数。"

#: 03310d98a52d4d41afc45cec45126b0f 46201cb6ff7c4d7e865d2905fdcf7286
#: driver.adxl34x.ADXL345.enable_tap_detection:3 of
#: unit.accel.AccelUnit.enable_tap_detection:3
msgid "1 to detect only single taps, and 2 to detect only double taps."
msgstr "1 用于仅检测单击，2 用于仅检测双击。"

#: 24aadc08a17a48ed9ccd0770f4ce45c1 5ab187dd965e4ca2bdca422fad2c80fe
#: driver.adxl34x.ADXL345.enable_tap_detection:6 of
#: unit.accel.AccelUnit.enable_tap_detection:6
msgid ""
"A threshold for the tap detection. The scale factor is 62.5 mg/LSB The "
"higher the value the less sensitive the detection."
msgstr "轻触检测的阈值。比例因子为 62.5 mg/LSB。数值越大，检测灵敏度越低。"

#: 37638e76bea34d119c779997c3e81829
#: driver.adxl34x.ADXL345.enable_tap_detection:10
#: f8f306caba6d46f49e9c36b2af93ba43 of
#: unit.accel.AccelUnit.enable_tap_detection:10
msgid ""
"This caps the duration of the impulse above ``threshold``. Anything above"
" ``duration`` won't register as a tap. The scale factor is 625 µs/LSB."
msgstr ""
"这将限制高于 ``threshold`` 的脉冲持续时间。任何超过 ``duration`` 的脉冲都不会被识别为一次轻触。缩放因子为 625 "
"µs/LSB。"

#: 0762d5bba01b4517883507d200cf8d13 881045d7b828494684003ca826140325
#: driver.adxl34x.ADXL345.enable_tap_detection:14 of
#: unit.accel.AccelUnit.enable_tap_detection:14
msgid ""
"(double tap only) The length of time after the initial impulse falls "
"below ``threshold`` to start the window looking for a second impulse. The"
" scale factor is 1.25 ms/LSB."
msgstr "（仅双击）在初始脉冲低于 ``threshold`` 后，到开始用于检测第二个脉冲的时间窗口之前的时长。比例因子为 1.25 ms/LSB。"

#: 3c5de386e9c3456ea39a31b7731e46af 67030738ffde4f23b54904bfb2a27fc0
#: driver.adxl34x.ADXL345.enable_tap_detection:19 of
#: unit.accel.AccelUnit.enable_tap_detection:19
msgid ""
"(double tap only) The length of the window in which to look for a second "
"tap. The scale factor is 1.25 ms/LSB."
msgstr "（仅双击）用于检测第二次点击的时间窗口长度。比例因子为 1.25 ms/LSB。"

